"{\"uid\": \"cyclingnews.com-races-olympic-games-2024-road-cycling-women-s-road-race-live-report\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  The silver and bronze went to Vos and Kopecky as Vas is edged out in three-up sprint  When you purchase through links on our site, we may earn an affiliate commission.Here's how it works.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 189, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympic Games 2024 - Everything you need to know  Paris Olympics: Women's Road Race - Preview  Paris 2024 Olympics road race course  Hello and bienvenue toCyclingnews' live coverage of the women's road race at the Paris Olympic Games!\", \"from\": 191, \"to\": 425, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The battle to succeed Anna Kiesenhofer of Austria as reigning Olympic Champion is due to start in just over an hour's time at 1410 CET, with 91 riders - including Kiesenhofer - in the 2024 Road Race peloton.\", \"from\": 427, \"to\": 634, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 449, \"end\": 465, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Kiesenhofer\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anna Kiesenhofer\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Kiesenhofer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Kiesenhofer\"}, {\"begin\": 469, \"end\": 476, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austria\", \"score\": 0.9994596842135979, \"rank\": 0.0005186725644578228, \"text\": \"Austria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Saturday's equivalent event for the Men road race culminated with a spectacular solo victory for Remco Evenepoel of Belgian, his second gold in just under a week.\", \"from\": 636, \"to\": 798, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 733, \"end\": 748, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Remco_Evenepoel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Remco Evenepoel\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Remco_Evenepoel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Remco_Evenepoel\"}, {\"begin\": 752, \"end\": 759, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"score\": 0.9986778326415714, \"rank\": 0.0012552176284166125, \"text\": \"Belgian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Laura Weislo reported on his post-race reaction here.Late puncture adds 'extra spice' to Remco Evenepoel's historic second Olympic gold medal performance  I think it is safe to say that Lotte Kopecky (BEL) i the big favourite.\", \"from\": 799, \"to\": 1025, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 799, \"end\": 804, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Laura\", \"score\": 0.7491816675644392, \"rank\": 0.28156908391928026, \"text\": \"Laura\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Laura\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Laura\"}, {\"begin\": 888, \"end\": 903, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Remco_Evenepoel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Remco Evenepoel\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Remco_Evenepoel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Remco_Evenepoel\"}, {\"begin\": 985, \"end\": 998, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lotte_Kopecky\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lotte Kopecky\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lotte_Kopecky\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lotte_Kopecky\"}, {\"begin\": 1000, \"end\": 1003, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"score\": 0.9999999981330348, \"rank\": 1.8314661706177629e-09, \"text\": \"BEL\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, she does not have the strongest team with Justine Ghekiere, Julie van de Velde and Margot Vanpachtenbeke in the squad.\", \"from\": 1026, \"to\": 1153, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1095, \"end\": 1113, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Julie_Van_de_Velde\", \"score\": 0.9999999999993179, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Julie van de Velde\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Julie_Van_de_Velde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Julie_Van_de_Velde\"}, {\"begin\": 1118, \"end\": 1124, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Margaret_of_Valois\", \"score\": 0.4983013876588794, \"rank\": 0.6668378262461465, \"text\": \"Margot\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Margaret_of_Valois\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Margaret_of_Valois\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It will be difficult for them to control the super four of the Netherlands.\", \"from\": 1154, \"to\": 1229, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1217, \"end\": 1228, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.7603963843765501, \"rank\": 0.3150099030399316, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With just under half an hour before the race starts, the first photos from sign on are coming in.\", \"from\": 1233, \"to\": 1330, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Beginning with the hosts, France.\", \"from\": 1331, \"to\": 1364, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1357, \"end\": 1363, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9989871391074417, \"rank\": 0.001012937982922414, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They bring the experience of Audrey Cordon-Ragot, the outside favourite of Julietta Labous and the national champion Victoire Berteau.\", \"from\": 1365, \"to\": 1499, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1394, \"end\": 1413, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Audrey_Cordon-Ragot\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Audrey Cordon-Ragot\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Audrey_Cordon-Ragot\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Audrey_Cordon-Ragot\"}, {\"begin\": 1440, \"end\": 1448, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Julietta\", \"score\": 0.9999999962433321, \"rank\": 3.5917493446183066e-09, \"text\": \"Julietta\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Julietta\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Julietta\"}, {\"begin\": 1482, \"end\": 1490, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Victoire_Conroy\", \"score\": 0.6982273599539999, \"rank\": 0.2919996904957694, \"text\": \"Victoire\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Victoire_Conroy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Victoire_Conroy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Silver and bronze in the men's road race, maybe another big result today?\", \"from\": 1500, \"to\": 1573, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is fantastic to see the two riders from Afghanistan lining up at the Olympic road race.\", \"from\": 1577, \"to\": 1667, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1620, \"end\": 1631, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\", \"score\": 0.9999984944988647, \"rank\": 1.0523832514611544e-06, \"text\": \"Afghanistan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The sisters, Fariba and Yulduz Hashimi.\", \"from\": 1668, \"to\": 1707, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1681, \"end\": 1687, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Behtash_Fariba\", \"score\": 0.999999999998