, \"to\": 2197, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2122, \"end\": 2129, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9601241308006399, \"rank\": 0.041354681288629916, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Either way, they have national champion Pfeiffer Georgi, London 2012 silver medalist Lizzie Deignan and ITT silver medalist Anna Henderson.\", \"from\": 2198, \"to\": 2337, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2238, \"end\": 2253, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pfeiffer_Georgi\", \"score\": 0.9999994495557681, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pfeiffer Georgi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pfeiffer_Georgi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pfeiffer_Georgi\"}, {\"begin\": 2255, \"end\": 2266, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999902481704, \"rank\": 9.74957019016544e-09, \"text\": \"London 2012\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2283, \"end\": 2297, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lizzie_Deignan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lizzie Deignan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lizzie_Deignan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lizzie_Deignan\"}, {\"begin\": 2302, \"end\": 2305, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Individual_time_trial\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.9335207342652514e-15, \"text\": \"ITT\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Individual_time_trial\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Individual_time_trial\"}, {\"begin\": 2322, \"end\": 2336, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Henderson\", \"score\": 0.9999958972008508, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anna Henderson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Henderson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Henderson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Team USA come to the race with Chloe Dygert and Kristen Faulkner.\", \"from\": 2339, \"to\": 2404, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2339, \"end\": 2347, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9585566867790996, \"rank\": 0.020067295575520627, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 2370, \"end\": 2382, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chlo\\u00e9_Dygert\", \"score\": 0.9999999166203714, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chloe Dygert\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chlo\\u00e9_Dygert\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chlo\\u00e9_Dygert\"}, {\"begin\": 2387, \"end\": 2403, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kristen_Faulkner\", \"score\": 0.9999993389976591, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kristen Faulkner\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kristen_Faulkner\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kristen_Faulkner\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Two excellent riders for a course like this and should not be counted out.\", \"from\": 2405, \"to\": 2479, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The riders have started the neutralised zone.\", \"from\": 2483, \"to\": 2528, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And the racing begins!!\", \"from\": 2532, \"to\": 2555, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Awa Bamogo (BKF)  Our person on the ground in Paris, Laura Weislo, spoke to Giro d'Italia women's champion, Elisa Longo-Borghini (ITA) before the start.\", \"from\": 2557, \"to\": 2709, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2557, \"end\": 2560, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Inwa\", \"score\": 0.8984542352890866, \"rank\": 0.11301703064904475, \"text\": \"Awa\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Inwa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Inwa\"}, {\"begin\": 2603, \"end\": 2608, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999973466357192, \"rank\": 2.653371296331833e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2610, \"end\": 2615, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/X-23\", \"score\": 0.764467540847644, \"rank\": 0.30717451295014686, \"text\": \"Laura\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/X-23\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/X-23\"}, {\"begin\": 2633, \"end\": 2646, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2009_Giro_d'Italia\", \"score\": 0.9536890268588967, \"rank\": 0.044948367197845875, \"text\": \"Giro d'Italia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2009_Giro_d'Italia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2009_Giro_d'Italia\"}, {\"begin\": 2687, \"end\": 2690, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"score\": 0.9988857457333944, \"rank\": 0.0005615967765174917, \"text\": \"ITA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Laura asked her about the men's race and Belgium's success with two potential winners.\", \"from\": 2711, \"to\": 2797, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2711, \"end\": 2716, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/X-23\", \"score\": 0.7644675408475572, \"rank\": 0.30717451295014686, \"text\": \"Laura\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/X-23\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/X-23\"}, {\"begin\": 2752, \"end\": 2759, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_Billie_Jean_King_Cup_team\", \"score\": 0.9963818306820992, \"rank\": 0.00351149529804334, \"text\": \"Belgium\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_Billie_Jean_King_Cup_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_Billie_Jean_King_Cup_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She said, \\\"We have four riders that are capable of anything a very fast one with [Elisa] Balsamo.\", \"from\": 2798, \"to\": 2895, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"an all rounder like me.\", \"from\": 2896, \"to\": 2919, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Silvia Persico is strong rider, a young one that can surprise everybody, and [Elena] Cecchini is somebody that has a lot of knowledge and experience so we are ready to fight and to do our operation.\\\"\", \"from\": 2920, \"to\": 3119, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2920, \"end\": 2934, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Silvia_Persico\", \"score\": 0.9999992216870242, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Silvia Persico\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Silvia_Persico\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Silvia_Persico\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On the form of her life, she summed up her feeling in one word: Determined.\", \"from\": 3121, \"to\": 3196, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Lizzie Deignan told Laura Weislo her preparation sucked - she broke her arm at the Tour of Flanders and she crashed in the Thuringen Tour last month.\", \"from\": 3200, \"to\": 3349, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3200, \"end\": 3214, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lizzie_Deignan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lizzie Deignan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lizzie_Deignan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lizzie_Deignan\"}, {\"begin\": 3220, \"end\": 3225, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Bush\", \"score\": 0.6069550627229812, \"rank\": 0.5106247181411273, \"text\": \"Laura\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Bush\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Bush\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 2012 silver medalist still has hopes for today, though.\", \"from\": 3351, \"to\": 3410, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I really believe that it's a wide open race and you know, there is pressure on my back.\", \"from\": 3411, \"to\": 3499, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have done everything I wanted to in my career.\", \"from\": 3500, \"to\": 3548, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Obviously Olympic gold is missing, but a silver medal is pretty hard to come by, too.\", \"from\": 3549, \"to\": 3634, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So I am just ready to enjoy myself.\\\"\", \"from\": 3635, \"to\": 3671, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She is in her last Olympics but will race on one more year with Lidl-Trek.\", \"from\": 3673, \"to\": 3747, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Kasia Niewiadoma - winner of La Fl\\u00e8che Wallonne - said it's been a very long build-up to today but she's very excited to get the race started.\", \"from\": 3751, \"to\": 3893, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3751, \"end\": 3767, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katarzyna_Niewiadoma\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kasia Niewiadoma\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katarzyna_Niewiadoma\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katarzyna_Niewiadoma\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am confident about my form.\", \"from\": 3895, \"to\": 3925, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Yet.\", \"from\": 3926, \"to\": 3930, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I also know that this race is going to be super open because it basically suits all of the riders.\", \"from\": 3931, \"to\": 4029, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So besides great shape, as we saw yesterday with Remco, you also need this little bit of luck to go in the right place.\", \"from\": 4030, \"to\": 4149, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I hope we will be able to find our moment.\\\"\", \"from\": 4150, \"to\": 4193, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Bamogo (BKF) has around 45\\\" over the peloton.\", \"from\": 4197, \"to\": 4242, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Onto the first climb of the day.\", \"from\": 4244, \"to\": 4276, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The C\\u00f4te des Gardes.\", \"from\": 4277, \"to\": 4297, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Nine catgorised climbs on today's route.\", \"from\": 4298, \"to\": 4338, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Bamogo (BKF) dragged back as the pace behind it too high for the rider from Burkina Faso.\", \"from\": 4339, \"to\": 4428, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4415, \"end\": 4427, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Burkina_Faso\", \"score\": 0.9999976594084607, \"rank\": 2.3405969520863538e-06, \"text\": \"Burkina Faso\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Burkina_Faso\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Burkina_Faso\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bamogo (BKF) has gone from out front to out of the back on this climb.\", \"from\": 4430, \"to\": 4500, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Houili (ALG)Al Sayegh (UAE)Ukpeseraye (NGR)Ingabire (RWA)  Minji Song (KOR)  Kim Cadzow (NZL)Rebecca Koerner (DEN)  All dragged back though.\", \"from\": 4502, \"to\": 4642, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4510, \"end\": 4513, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ALG_Spor\", \"score\": 0.749540405054385, \"rank\": 0.22297885643417617, \"text\": \"ALG\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ALG_Spor\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ALG_Spor\"}, {\"begin\": 4573, \"end\": 4576, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asteroid_family\", \"score\": 0.9531012611247015, \"rank\": 0.046718031443476346, \"text