": 0.9999999982652525, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Antri Christoforou\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antri_Christoforou\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antri_Christoforou\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nora Jen\\u010du\\u0161ov\\u00e1 (SVK)  She has a small gap on the bunch.\", \"from\": 4731, \"to\": 4786, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4731, \"end\": 4735, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nora_Fries\", \"score\": 0.8742980158524546, \"rank\": 0.1337706836741604, \"text\": \"Nora\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nora_Fries\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nora_Fries\"}, {\"begin\": 4747, \"end\": 4750, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbian_Army_of_Krajina\", \"score\": 0.7915209656135116, \"rank\": 0.2631342365421323, \"text\": \"SVK\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbian_Army_of_Krajina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbian_Army_of_Krajina\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cecilie Uttrup Ludwig (Denmark) was all smiles at the start, saying, \\\"Super excited.\", \"from\": 4788, \"to\": 4872, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4788, \"end\": 4809, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cecilie_Uttrup_Ludwig\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cecilie Uttrup Ludwig\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cecilie_Uttrup_Ludwig\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cecilie_Uttrup_Ludwig\"}, {\"begin\": 4811, \"end\": 4818, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denmark\", \"score\": 0.9993502761180784, \"rank\": 0.00030826868237111073, \"text\": \"Denmark\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denmark\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denmark\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yeah, we are at the Olympics, we are in front of the Eiffel Tower - it does not get much better.\\\"\", \"from\": 4873, \"to\": 4970, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She had a crash in the TT but is OK and hoping to keep it upright today.\", \"from\": 4972, \"to\": 5044, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4995, \"end\": 4997, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isle_of_Man_TT\", \"score\": 0.9373860383797291, \"rank\": 0.05568064858582807, \"text\": \"TT\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isle_of_Man_TT\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isle_of_Man_TT\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think it's going to be super, super hard course.\", \"from\": 5045, \"to\": 5096, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"it might be difficult to make the difference on the climbs, but as we saw yesterday, there is probably going to be some lulls after climbs where there might be some attacks so you just got to be eyes open on the circuit.\\\"\", \"from\": 5097, \"to\": 5318, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"New Zealand's Kim Cadzow: \\\"I am just really excited to get out there and race.\", \"from\": 5320, \"to\": 5398, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5334, \"end\": 5337, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Craig\", \"score\": 0.9471440718348311, \"rank\": 0.04988435346902889, \"text\": \"Kim\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Craig\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Craig\"}, {\"begin\": 5338, \"end\": 5344, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cadzow_Castle\", \"score\": 0.9964949128715481, \"rank\": 0.0035155380348218025, \"text\": \"Cadzow\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cadzow_Castle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cadzow_Castle\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think it's completely unpredictable, and so it's gonna be a lot of fun.\", \"from\": 5399, \"to\": 5472, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think the woman's race always plays out a little bit differently to the men's but be some early breaks, early attacks and then it's just going to be a chaotic final.\", \"from\": 5474, \"to\": 5642, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think it's gonna be hard, especially with some of the bigger nations but I will give it my best and me and Niamh [Fisher-Black] will try and outfox them.\\\"\", \"from\": 5644, \"to\": 5801, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5754, \"end\": 5759, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Niamh_Cusack\", \"score\": 0.9999477039543232, \"rank\": 5.145879066186473e-05, \"text\": \"Niamh\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Niamh_Cusack\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Niamh_Cusack\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mavi Garcia (Spain) coming off a top 10 overall in the Giro d'Italia was surprised by the men's race, she thought there would be a big group coming to the finish but was pleased to see the race broke up.\", \"from\": 5805, \"to\": 6008, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5805, \"end\": 5816, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Margarita_Victoria_Garc\\u00eda\", \"score\": 0.9999999439647824, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mavi Garcia\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Margarita_Victoria_Garc\\u00eda\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Margarita_Victoria_Garc\\u00eda\"}, {\"begin\": 5818, \"end\": 5823, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8361012858868687, \"rank\": 0.1147366164282491, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's good news for me because I am strong but not [a sprinter].\", \"from\": 6010, \"to\": 6074, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I think the race is really hard in the final, the climbs are not long but it's a hard circuit and I like it.\\\"\", \"from\": 6075, \"to\": 6184, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ashleigh Moolman-Pasio (South Africa) is coming off a fractured vertebra from a crash in the Volta a Catalunya in early June.\", \"from\": 6188, \"to\": 6313, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6212, \"end\": 6224, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9999956680902109, \"rank\": 2.2656840903364587e-06, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She had a smooth recovery and did a lot of preparation on Zwift.\", \"from\": 6314, \"to\": 6378, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6372, \"end\": 6377, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zwift\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Zwift\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zwift\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zwift\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She said it is \\\"surreal\\\" and \\\"feels like I am in a dream\\\" because she did not expect to make it here.\", \"from\": 6380, \"to\": 6481, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She's got high ambitions for today.\", \"from\": 6482, \"to\": 6517, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's obviously a really tricky city circuit it's a bit like a criterium.\", \"from\": 6519, \"to\": 6592, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For me, obviously, it would be ideal to get into a breakaway before that city circuit.\", \"from\": 6593, \"to\": 6679, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We saw yesterday that there was a medal from the breakaway so I think that's a really good opportunity and that's what I will be looking for today.\\\"\", \"from\": 6680, \"to\": 6828, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Nora Jen\\u010du\\u0161ov\\u00e1 (SVK) has around 45\\\" on the peloton currently led by Afghanistan, Switzerland and Germany.\", \"from\": 6832, \"to\": 6937, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6832, \"end\": 6836, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_The_Flash_characters\", \"score\": 0.8646825335204884, \"rank\": 0.14935567962616864, \"text\": \"Nora\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_The_Flash_characters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_The_Flash_characters\"}, {\"begin\": 6848, \"end\": 6851, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbian_Army_of_Krajina\", \"score\": 0.946317763021989, \"rank\": 0.05665407254418645, \"text\": \"SVK\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbian_Army_of_Krajina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbian_Army_of_Krajina\"}, {\"begin\": 6900, \"end\": 6911, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\", \"score\": 0.9778683589484962, \"rank\": 0.015930785896577794, \"text\": \"Afghanistan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\"}, {\"begin\": 6913, \"end\": 6924, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\", \"score\": 0.8074748698732925, \"rank\": 0.22704962629654302, \"text\": \"Switzerland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\"}, {\"begin\": 6929, \"end\": 6936, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nazi_Germany\", \"score\": 0.6314903514649683, \"rank\": 0.5443137214758815, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nazi_Germany\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nazi_Germany\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fariba Hashimi (AFG)  She is trying to bridge over to Jen\\u010du\\u0161ov\\u00e1 (SVK).\", \"from\": 6939, \"to\": 7009, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6939, \"end\": 6945, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Behtash_Fariba\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Fariba\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Behtash_Fariba\", \"db