_Lach\", \"score\": 0.9999991854079915, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Marta Lach\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marta_Lach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marta_Lach\"}, {\"begin\": 22966, \"end\": 22969, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polish_language\", \"score\": 0.7479819562947165, \"rank\": 0.3365494852013667, \"text\": \"POL\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polish_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polish_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's a dream come true...\", \"from\": 23028, \"to\": 23054, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's the best feeling in the world.\", \"from\": 23055, \"to\": 23090, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not know how to describe it.\\\"\", \"from\": 23091, \"to\": 23125, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We can not have an Olympic road race without this stunning shot as Faulkner (USA) crossed the line and took gold.\", \"from\": 23129, \"to\": 23242, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"An amazing moment for Faulkner and the USA.\", \"from\": 23246, \"to\": 23289, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 23268, \"end\": 23276, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Faulkner\", \"score\": 0.9996170386952389, \"rank\": 0.0003156057905628845, \"text\": \"Faulkner\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Faulkner\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Faulkner\"}, {\"begin\": 23285, \"end\": 23288, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.926572399914827, \"rank\": 0.0791531131134264, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\ud83e\\udd47\\ud83c\\uddfa\\ud83c\\uddf8 Kristen Faulkner \\ud83c\\uddfa\\ud83c\\uddf8\\ud83e\\udd47Women's #CyclingRoad Olympic Champion \\ud83d\\udd25#Cycling #OlympicCycling #Paris2024 pic.twitter.com/fKkaCRTOxcAugust 4, 2024  Kristen Faulkner (USA) after the finish:  \\\"I feel like it's a dream come true.\", \"from\": 23291, \"to\": 23510, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 23315, \"end\": 23317, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_the_United_States\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"\\ud83c\\uddfa\\ud83c\\uddf8\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_the_United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 23439, \"end\": 23455, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kristen_Faulkner\", \"score\": 0.9999993389976591, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kristen Faulkner\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kristen_Faulkner\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kristen_Faulkner\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I took a really big risk a few years ago to come to pursue my dream and I made it happen.\", \"from\": 23511, \"to\": 23600, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's the best feeling in the world, I do not know how to describe it.\\\"\", \"from\": 23601, \"to\": 23671, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Did you hope to win solo?\", \"from\": 23673, \"to\": 23698, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I had high hopes.\", \"from\": 23700, \"to\": 23718, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am racing team pursuit in two days and so I said I'd only do the road race if I felt strong and felt I had a chance of a medal.\", \"from\": 23719, \"to\": 23848, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I knew that it would be a really tough race but if I was racing, I was racing to win.\", \"from\": 23849, \"to\": 23934, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That was a promise I made to my team pursuit teammates.\\\"\", \"from\": 23935, \"to\": 23991, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What was the plan with the final?\", \"from\": 23993, \"to\": 24026, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I knew that Kopeckly wanted to catch the front two, so I knew she'd ride with me.\", \"from\": 24028, \"to\": 24110, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I also knew that if we caught them, then I had to attack because I could not beat any of them at the line.\", \"from\": 24111, \"to\": 24217, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I knew the best place to attack was right after we caught them and everyone was tied.\", \"from\": 24218, \"to\": 24303, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That was my chance.\", \"from\": 24304, \"to\": 24323, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I practised my late attack several times this year, so I felt pretty comfortable with how to do it.\", \"from\": 24324, \"to\": 24423, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I just hoped it worked.\\\"\", \"from\": 24424, \"to\": 24448, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Did you know you'd won?\", \"from\": 24450, \"to\": 24473, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was pretty sure I'd won but it was like 'what in the world just happened?'\", \"from\": 24475, \"to\": 24552, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I could not process it.\", \"from\": 24553, \"to\": 24576, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It took me a few minutes.\", \"from\": 24577, \"to\": 24602, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I had to double and triple check that I won gold.\", \"from\": 24603, \"to\": 24652, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I knew it but I did not know it.\\\"\", \"from\": 24653, \"to\": 24686, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Make sure you have a read of our post race report by clicking the link below...  >>>Paris Olympics: Kristen Faulkner shocks favourites with solo victory in women's road race    In Bronze, Lotte Kopecky (Belgium).\", \"from\": 24690, \"to\": 24902, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 24781, \"end\": 24795, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 24797, \"end\": 24813, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kristen_Faulkner\", \"score\": 0.9999993389976591, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kristen Faulkner\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kristen_Faulkner\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kristen_Faulkner\"}, {\"begin\": 24885, \"end\": 24898, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lotte_Kopecky\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lotte Kopecky\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lotte_Kopecky\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lotte_Kopecky\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In Silver.\", \"from\": 24906, \"to\": 24916, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Marianne Vos (Netherlands) with a brilliant performance.\", \"from\": 24917, \"to\": 24973, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 24924, \"end\": 24936, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marianne_Vos\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Marianne Vos\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marianne_Vos\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marianne_Vos\"}, {\"begin\": 24924, \"end\": 24936, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marianne_Vos\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Marianne Vos\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marianne_Vos\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marianne_Vos\"}, {\"begin\": 24938, \"end\": 24949, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.9684184111228186, \"rank\": 0.031915788573541035, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.or